{
  "stem": "18778.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the little boy and I who were living with our foster family, we were sleeping in a double bed together, and I said to him-- his name was Eddie-- I said, Eddie, put on your gas mask.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We put on our gas masks and went back to sleep.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And in the mornings, when the landlady came to wake us up, she screeched because there are these two little monsters in the bed with their gas masks on.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But we really didn't notice there was much of a war going on that first year.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I went to London twice to visit my parents, once at Hanukkah time and once at Pesach time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And in May, I think things turned around completely.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was the Battle of Dunkirk, when the British officers were all at the ascot races.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And Hitler could have taken England at that time without batting an eyelash.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I think only because of his astrologers advised him against it, this didn't happen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But all of a sudden, first of all, the German and Austrian males were rounded up and interned.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They were interned mostly on the Isle of Man in camps.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Because the British claim that there were German spies posing as Jewish refugees amongst them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they just put the whole lot-- interned them, isolated them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They didn't mistreat them, but they were not free.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "At that time, it was almost the end of the school year, and I went back to London to join my mother.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "She was all by herself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I had earned myself some extra money by helping the farmers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "All of us did that.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
